            "due_date": "<dd><p> 16/10/2026 2:00 pm</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>It is each student's responsibility to COMPLETE the submission BEFORE 2PM (14:00:00) of the due date via the Blackboard TurnitIn submission portal.</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": null,
